# SkillForge environment guide
#
# This root file is documentation only; neither application loads it.
# Keep client-safe and server-secret configuration separate:
#
#   Copy-Item client/.env.example client/.env.local
#   Copy-Item server/.env.example server/.env
#
# Only NEXT_PUBLIC_ values may appear in client/.env.local. Supabase server
# secret (or legacy service-role), OpenAI, and OpenRouter API keys belong only
# in server/.env. The AI Assist provider order is OpenAI -> OpenRouter -> a
# deterministic fallback.
#
# See docs/IMPLEMENTATION_ROADMAP.md for the credential gates and
# docs/HACKATHON_BUILD_LOG.md for the current integration status.
